There are four different techniques to create multi-column layouts. Each technique has its pros and cons:

1.CSS framework - Bootstrap & W3.CSS
2.CSS float property -as long as you know float and clear - Disadvantages: Floating elements are tied to the document
 flow, which may harm the flexibility.
3.CSS flexbox - elements behave more predictably
4.CSS grid

